{
  "stem": "3757.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I-- I saw, now they will take us and-- and killing on the-- in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But they left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So later, we heard that somebody shot, maybe from this building.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "This-- this building-- it was very interesting why they made out of it a Jewish building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was next to the Hungarian parliament on the shore of the Danube, four buildings-- such a block.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In this building, facing the parliament, lived the newspaper owner-- the biggest Nazi, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then, on the other building, what faced the Danube, they were-- they put up a German office of full with German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They always loved it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They looked over to my building so to-- to my star.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were on the street.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the fourth building was a regular apartment house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this was designated a small building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was not the real reason why to make for this a building where a lot of people can move in because they said that the English whoever comes to bomb Budapest, they will know that in this building are Jewish, and we will save the Germans [LAUGHS] and-- and [NON-ENGLISH] there.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But really, they didn't bomb this building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think they didn't want to ruin the parliament.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on the 16th, I didn't know what-- what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to save only the child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't care about myself, only the child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I couldn't find a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before that, I tried-- I took a-- there were small balconies on the buildings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the next hall, where this Nazi lived, it was-- there was wrought iron gates.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I tried to put over a ironing board.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe I can somehow escape on that some night.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
